<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1748346-this-is-a-1914-book-surely-there-must-be">This is a 1914 book. Surely there must be public domain translation by now. But I can&#39;t find any, not in French, not in English.
The language is above me and I&#39;d like to read both languages, to check faster than with a dictionnary. 

Where can I find a public domain translation?</a>
</div>
