              <span id="reviewTextContainer2494669818" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11068530858146529794">A rare gift of a book, a magical tour de force about the close friendship between a man and his donkey. Heartbreaking and mesmerizing at once, the story is set in a small rural town in Spain in the early part of the twentieth century. The linked poems, originally written in Spanish, have been translated into many languages.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


