        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer22511984" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1828453851817189752">This book gave such a wonderful picture of Spain in that era. The innocence of the children, the beauty of nature and the bonding and love a person has with their animal. I love Platero who is so soft, he feels like he has no bones when you hug him; yet he is so tough, hard-working and strong. The short essays are tremendously sweet and beautifully descriptive. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


