<span id="freeTextContainer13504851703173425193">The version of this book that I read was translated by Eloise Roach. These wonderful prose poems cover a year of insights and observations that Juan Ramon Jimenez made while recuperating in Andalusia from depression after his father died. Roach&apos;s version has some delightful drawings by Jo Alys Downs that add to the over all book.</span>
  <span id="freeText13504851703173425193" style="display:none">The version of this book that I read was translated by Eloise Roach. These wonderful prose poems cover a year of insights and observations that Juan Ramon Jimenez made while recuperating in Andalusia from depression after his father died. Roach's version has some delightful drawings by Jo Alys Downs that add to the over all book.</span>
