<div id="review_1513805930" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1513805930" />
    <a title="Scott Cox" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21638774-scott-cox"><img alt="Scott Cox" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1436633517p2/21638774.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1513805930?book_show_action=true">Jan 17, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Scott Cox" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Scott Cox" href="/user/show/21638774-scott-cox">Scott Cox</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780595003457" href="/book/show/1082371.Platero_and_I">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21638774-scott-cox?shelf=nobel-prize">nobel-prize</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21638774-scott-cox?shelf=european-literature">european-literature</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21638774-scott-cox?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21638774-scott-cox?shelf=literature">literature</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1513805930" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7058607803974177745">These endearing stories by Spanish Nobel laureate Juan Ramon Jimenez are a series of monologues between a man and his donkey (Platero); as well as with Diana the Goat and a parrot who&apos;s only words are &quot;Ce n&apos;est rien&quot; (it is nothing). These stories are really something! I also recommend reading Juan Ramon Jimenez&apos;s selected poems &amp; prose, &quot;Light and Shadows.&quot; The following is one of my favorites &quot;Even though my soul fits so wonderfully inside my body - like a clear idea in a line perfect for it -</span>
  <span id="freeText7058607803974177745" style="display:none">These endearing stories by Spanish Nobel laureate Juan Ramon Jimenez are a series of monologues between a man and his donkey (Platero); as well as with Diana the Goat and a parrot who's only words are "Ce n'est rien" (it is nothing). These stories are really something! I also recommend reading Juan Ramon Jimenez's selected poems &amp; prose, "Light and Shadows." The following is one of my favorites "Even though my soul fits so wonderfully inside my body - like a clear idea in a line perfect for it - nevertheless it has to abandon the body eventually, leaving it like some academic's line, hollow and stiff!"</span>
  <a data-text-id="7058607803974177745" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


