<span id="freeTextContainer9892566061404768698">So charming that it inspired me to go and wander Moguer, eat and drink its soul in bread and orange wine, pay homage at Ximenez’s childhood home, and then learn Spanish. Soon I will re-read this book in the language in which it was written. It’s that lovely. </span>

